query: SELECT a.id as acctId, a.accountName, a.accountPlan, a.accountStatus, a.accountOwnerUserId, u.name as ownerName, u.email as ownerEmail, s.subStatus, p.planKey as subPlanKey FROM accounts a JOIN users u ON u.id = a.accountOwnerUserId LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON s.subAccountId = a.id LEFT JOIN plans p ON p.id = s.subPlanId ORDER BY a.id
